    <h2>How to Keep Your Bill Low in 2026</h2>
    <p>The single most effective strategy is staying under the 200-unit threshold to maintain Protected status. Beyond that, shifting heavy appliances (washing machines, irons, dishwashers) to off-peak hours (before 6:30 PM or after 10:30 PM) avoids peak surcharges for consumers with sanctioned load above 5kW. Read our complete guide: <a href="/blog/how-to-reduce-electricity-bill/">15 Proven Tips to Reduce Your Pakistan Electricity Bill</a>.</p>

